三.函数的兼容性
函数的兼容性主要是比较参数和返回值

参数

  let sum1 = (a: string, b: string) => a + b;
  let sum2 = (a: string) => a;
  sum1 = sum2

赋值函数的参数要少于等于被赋值的函数，与对象相反,例如:

  type Func = (item: T, index: number) => void
  function forEach(arr: T[], cb: Func) {
      for (let i = 0; i  {
      console.log(item);
  });

返回值

  type sum1 = () => string | number
  type sum2 = () => string;

  let fn1: sum1;
  let fn2!: sum2;
